CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1960, pg. A9 reads: "Fourth Prize - Or honorable mention, went to Epsilon Chapter of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority, for its table, featuring home-made cookies. Left to right: Anita Williams, Mary L. Stone and Eva M. Thomas, Food Festival chairman. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Anita Williams, Mary L. Stone, and Eva M. Thomas, standing behind Delta Sigma Theta table with dishes of food, in Penn Sheraton Hotel for Brotherhood Food Festival
